Retrieve a list of traffic events from today.

Retrieve a list of traffic events from today.

traffic_events(status = "ACTIVE", headline = NA, event_type = NA,
  severity = NA, updated = NA, schedule = NA, limit = 10000)

Arguments

status

Default 'ALL'.
headline

Summary of event.
event_type

Type of event such as CONSTRUCTION, SPECIAL_EVENT
severity

level of severity of event. Note this is usually UNKNOWN
updated

UTC timestamp of event updated on or after.
schedule

UTC timestamp of times event is active
limit

Limiting number of events to return

Value

Dataframe of events filtered to parameters passed

Examples

traffic_events()
